---
import ImageComparison from "../React/ImageComparison";
---
<section class="bg-white pt-20 text-base-900">
  <div class="px-8 py-20 mx-auto md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 space-y-4">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight"
      >
        惊人的边缘处理效果
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg">
        我们的 AI
        已经学习了数百万张图片，能够精准区分前景与背景，甚至包括最难处理的发丝和透明物体。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 1. 左右滑动对比组件 -->
    <div class="mb-24">
      <ImageComparison client:visible />
      <div
        class="flex justify-center mt-6 space-x-8 text-sm font-bold text-slate-400"
      >
        <span class="flex items-center"
          ><i class="fas fa-image mr-2"></i> 原图</span
        >
        <span class="flex items-center"
          ><i class="fas fa-magic mr-2 text-indigo-600"></i> AI 处理后</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2. 三种场景平铺对比 -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
      <!-- 场景 A：电商产品 -->
      <div class="sample-card group">
        <div
          class="relative h-64 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden mb-6 shadow-md bg-slate-200"
        >
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
            alt="原图"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full transparent-bg flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
          >
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
              alt="结果"
              class="w-4/5 object-contain filter drop-shadow-2xl"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-black/60 text-white text-[10px] px-2 py-1 rounded-md uppercase font-bold tracking-widest backdrop-blur-sm"
          >
            鼠标悬停看效果
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">电商产品</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
          精准处理鞋子、包袋及电子产品边缘，生成的图片可直接用于上架展示。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 场景 B：人像抠图 -->
      <div class="sample-card group">
        <div
          class="relative h-64 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden mb-6 shadow-md bg-slate-200"
        >
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
            alt="原图"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full transparent-bg flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
          >
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
              alt="结果"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              style="mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 60%, transparent 100%);"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-black/60 text-white text-[10px] px-2 py-1 rounded-md uppercase font-bold tracking-widest backdrop-blur-sm"
          >
            发丝级切割
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">人像写真</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
          不再为凌乱的发丝烦恼。无论是自拍还是模特图，都能完美分离主体。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 场景 C：动物/毛绒 -->
      <div class="sample-card group">
        <div
          class="relative h-64 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden mb-6 shadow-md bg-slate-200"
        >
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514888286974-6c03e2ca1dba?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
            alt="原图"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full transparent-bg flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
          >
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514888286974-6c03e2ca1dba?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
              alt="结果"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              style="mask-image: linear-gradient(to top, transparent, black);"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">动物与宠物</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
          处理宠物的细毛边缘是一项挑战，但对我们的 AI 来说轻而易举。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
